content: Reminds me of being in limbo… I wrote about this the other day. https://medium.com/@drehutchinson/limbo-4cec366b1531?source=linkShare-3784638099a6-1491842935 I found its a part of life…not the highlights that people talk about and share, but its really what makes use comfortable with ourselves and the choices we have and will make. Keep looking in mum…it will reenforce your soul.
